Lunarpine falls back from the ramming he recieved leaving a small 
trench where he skid along the ground.

"I'll take that as a no to the surrender."

Lunarpine dropped his rifle in the collision so all he had left was 
his claws,"So you want this battle up close and personal. suits me 
fine, I just gotta warn you that rams are prey to us wolves, and I 
just love the taste."

Lunarpine rises to his feat and charges forward with his claws raised 
slashing at Ares.
